{"storyMeta":{"storyReviewType":"NONE","storyId":"act34side_level_act34side_06_end","storyGroup":"act34side","storySort":13,"storyDependence":"act34side_level_act34side_06_beg","storyCanShow":1,"storyCode":"BP-6","storyName":"阿戈尔失格","storyPic":null,"storyInfo":"乌尔比安突入弥利亚留姆信标塔的中控室。面对曾经是挚友，如今却追求与海嗣“共生共荣”的堕落者，乌尔比安审判了他。","storyCanEnter":1,"storyTxt":"activities/act34side/level_act34side_06_end","avgTag":"行动后","unLockType":"STAGE_CLEAR","costItemType":"NONE","costItemId":null,"costItemCount":0,"stageCount":1,"requiredStages":[{"stageId":"act34side_06","minState":"PASS","maxState":"COMPLETE"}],"prev":11,"next":13,"characters":["布兰都斯","乌尔比安"]},"lines":[{"type":"header","key":"title_test","skippable":"true","mode":"BLACK_MASK","id":0},{"type":"stopmusic","id":1},{"type":"dialog","id":2},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":3},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":4},{"type":"charslot","id":5},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/ef/Avg_bg_51_g8_oldinstitute.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":6},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$loneliness_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/static/m_avg/m_avg_loneliness_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":7,"musicid":0},{"type":"cameraeffect","effect":"Grayscale","amount":"0.8","keep":"true","id":8},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":9},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":10},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","focus":"r","id":11},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_clothmovement","volume":"1","id":12},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_4145_Ulpia_1#1$1","posfrom":"0,-50","posto":"0,0","duration":"1.5","isblock":"true","id":13},{"type":"delay","time":"0.8","id":14},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"1","id":15},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1381_1#8$1","posfrom":"-200,0","posto":"0,0","duration":"1.5","id":16},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":17},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1381_1#8$1","focus":"l","id":18},{"type":"dialogue","name":"布兰都斯","text":"啊，你醒了？","id":19,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4e/Avg_avg_npc_1381_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"布兰都斯","text":"伤口我已经帮你处理过了。旁边有两支神经活性剂，能让你快速恢复精神。我来注射，还是交给小帮手？","id":20,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4e/Avg_avg_npc_1381_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_4145_Ulpia_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":21},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"......","id":22},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1381_1#10$1","focus":"l","id":23},{"type":"dialogue","name":"布兰都斯","text":"好吧，你自己来。","id":24,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/07/Avg_avg_npc_1381_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":25},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":26},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1381_1#8$1","focus":"l","id":27},{"type":"dialogue","name":"布兰都斯","text":"......动作真熟练，看起来恢复得不错。","id":28,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4e/Avg_avg_npc_1381_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1381_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":29},{"type":"dialogue","name":"布兰都斯","text":"虽然劝也没用，但我还是得多说一句。","id":30,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/0b/Avg_avg_npc_1381_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"布兰都斯","text":"你不能一直在自己身上做实验，不然光戴上面罩还不够，你得把眼睛也遮住，才能不至于看起来像受过虐待。","id":31,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/0b/Avg_avg_npc_1381_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_4145_Ulpia_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":32},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"我的着装习惯与改造实验无关。","id":33},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1381_1#8$1","focus":"l","id":34},{"type":"dialogue","name":"布兰都斯","text":"也是，你一直是这副模样。当年你只要阴暗地走进教室坐下，就足够让我们所有人打个寒战了。","id":35,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4e/Avg_avg_npc_1381_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"布兰都斯","text":"我们认识这么多年，我平时都见不到你的脸。","id":36,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4e/Avg_avg_npc_1381_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_4145_Ulpia_1#8$1","focus":"r","id":37},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"布兰都斯，你既然开起了玩笑，看来结果并不算糟糕？","id":38},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1381_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":39},{"type":"dialogue","name":"布兰都斯","text":"很难用糟不糟糕来评价，我刚刚的情绪体验，就像是西昆妲闭着眼睛开巡逻舰，而我坐在她旁边一样——天翻地覆。","id":40,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/0b/Avg_avg_npc_1381_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_4145_Ulpia_1#3$1","focus":"r","id":41},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"......","id":42},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1381_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":43},{"type":"dialogue","name":"布兰都斯","text":"起初，我观察到自适应接点技术产生了预料之外的效果......","id":44,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/0b/Avg_avg_npc_1381_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"布兰都斯","text":"你的身体没有像预期中那样，在海嗣基因表现出异常的性状控制力时，加强对海嗣基因的排斥。排异的表现反而有所减轻。","id":45,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/0b/Avg_avg_npc_1381_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_4145_Ulpia_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":46},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"这意味着我的海嗣化进程正在加快？","id":47},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1381_1#8$1","focus":"l","id":48},{"type":"dialogue","name":"布兰都斯","text":"不，恰恰相反。","id":49,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4e/Avg_avg_npc_1381_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"布兰都斯","text":"就在准备中断手术的时候，我观察到了奇妙的现象。在你身体的排异反应减轻之后，海嗣基因也放缓了对你的性状控制。","id":50,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4e/Avg_avg_npc_1381_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"布兰都斯","text":"简直就好像——你的身体与海嗣的基因达成了某种共识。","id":51,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4e/Avg_avg_npc_1381_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_4145_Ulpia_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":52},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"这种现象有进一步研究的价值。不过现在，我需要知道，这种情况是否会影响深海猎人接下来的作战。","id":53},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"斩杀“初生”，这将会是深海猎人诞生以来最重要的一次行动。","id":54},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"在这个时间节点上，我不允许出现任何变故。","id":55},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1381_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":56},{"type":"dialogue","name":"布兰都斯","text":"目前还没有观察到负面的影响，在你们出发之前，我会继续安排几次安全性测试。","id":57,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/0b/Avg_avg_npc_1381_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"布兰都斯","text":"不过，要真正摸清这种现象背后的原理，最好是你能活着回来，帮我做进一步的研究。","id":58,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/0b/Avg_avg_npc_1381_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1381_1#5$1","focus":"l","id":59},{"type":"dialogue","name":"布兰都斯","text":"说实话，我很不放心。","id":60,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d4/Avg_avg_npc_1381_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"布兰都斯","text":"毕竟我们从来没有发起过如此规模的战争，将所有的深海猎人，三支完整的正规军团，派往一处海沟......","id":61,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d4/Avg_avg_npc_1381_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_4145_Ulpia_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":62},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"没有这样的一场战争，我们如何斩杀海嗣的生代，它们的源头，它们的“神”？","id":63},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1381_1#10$1","focus":"l","id":64},{"type":"dialogue","name":"布兰都斯","text":"你真的相信我们能就此一劳永逸地解决海嗣问题吗？","id":65,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/07/Avg_avg_npc_1381_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_4145_Ulpia_1#8$1","focus":"r","id":66},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"哪怕已经与我们共事十多年，你还是没有消除对深海猎人计划的怀疑。","id":67},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1381_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":68},{"type":"dialogue","name":"布兰都斯","text":"你要听实话吗？","id":69,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/0b/Avg_avg_npc_1381_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_4145_Ulpia_1#8$1","focus":"r","id":70},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"......","id":71},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1381_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":72},{"type":"dialogue","name":"布兰都斯","text":"说实话，这种以扭曲演化的轨迹、牺牲同胞的人性为前提的计划，在审核阶段就应该被驳回。","id":73,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/0b/Avg_avg_npc_1381_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"布兰都斯","text":"若不是因为你，我根本不会去考虑它的可行性，更不可能为它付出十多年的努力。","id":74,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/0b/Avg_avg_npc_1381_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"布兰都斯","text":"......既然已经身陷其中，那么越是怀疑，我越要成为最核心的参与者，亲手掌控它的走向。","id":75,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/0b/Avg_avg_npc_1381_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1381_1#2$1","focus":"l","id":76},{"type":"dialogue","name":"布兰都斯","text":"但我还是忘不掉，这间研究所创造出了多少“怪物”。","id":77,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/04/Avg_avg_npc_1381_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"布兰都斯","text":"他们大多数由你亲手处决，乌尔比安。","id":78,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/04/Avg_avg_npc_1381_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_4145_Ulpia_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":79},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"是。","id":80},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1381_1#7$1","focus":"l","id":81},{"type":"dialogue","name":"布兰都斯","text":"他们的死甚至算不上“牺牲”，对吧？","id":82,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/df/Avg_avg_npc_1381_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_4145_Ulpia_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":83},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"被海嗣摧毁了家园，夺去了生命的阿戈尔人更多。","id":84},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"布兰都斯，这样的辩论我们进行了很多遍，没有必要在临行前再来一次。","id":85},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"尽快安排安全性测试吧。另外，正在进行中的深海猎人改造实验也需要全部暂停。","id":86},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1381_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":87},{"type":"dialogue","name":"布兰都斯","text":"你的意思是？","id":88,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/0b/Avg_avg_npc_1381_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_4145_Ulpia_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":89},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"没有猎人在场的情况下，实验中如果出现任何异样，会很难处理。","id":90},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1381_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":91},{"type":"dialogue","name":"布兰都斯","text":"“异样”。","id":92,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/0b/Avg_avg_npc_1381_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":93},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":94},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1381_1#10$1","focus":"l","id":95},{"type":"dialogue","name":"布兰都斯","text":"乌尔比安，十多年来，深海猎人计划始终由你主持，但你自己同样无法完全信任它，对吗？","id":96,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/07/Avg_avg_npc_1381_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"布兰都斯","text":"这才是你选择做第一个受试者的理由。","id":97,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/07/Avg_avg_npc_1381_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"布兰都斯","text":"这场战役能否一劳永逸地解决海嗣危机，你其实也没有十足的把握。","id":98,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/07/Avg_avg_npc_1381_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_4145_Ulpia_1#4$1","focus":"r","id":99},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"布兰都斯......","id":100},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1381_1#8$1","focus":"l","id":101},{"type":"dialogue","name":"布兰都斯","text":"不，乌尔比安，时至今日，我比谁都期待这场战役能够取得胜利。","id":102,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4e/Avg_avg_npc_1381_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"布兰都斯","text":"或许等你们平安返航的时候，深海猎人计划已经没有存在的必要。到时候，我们甚至可以重新拾起曾经的研究项目。","id":103,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4e/Avg_avg_npc_1381_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"布兰都斯","text":"你是不是都快忘了？之前在评议会上，我还遇见了我们的导师。他还问起了我们的理想。","id":104,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4e/Avg_avg_npc_1381_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_4145_Ulpia_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":105},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"“阿戈尔细胞演变史”。","id":106},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1381_1#9$1","focus":"l","id":107},{"type":"dialogue","name":"布兰都斯","text":"不是多么宏大的课题，但从一个微小的切面审视我们自身的源流，我坚信那是一种美的追求。","id":108,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/eb/Avg_avg_npc_1381_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"布兰都斯","text":"从千万年前在江河中摆动附肢的先祖，到如今在此畅谈科学与理想的你我，这之中蕴藏着一种内在秩序的流变。","id":109,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/eb/Avg_avg_npc_1381_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1381_1#8$1","focus":"l","id":110},{"type":"dialogue","name":"布兰都斯","text":"乌尔比安，或许我们还有机会见证它？","id":111,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4e/Avg_avg_npc_1381_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":112},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":113},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":114},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":115},{"type":"charslot","id":116},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/8a/Avg_bg_51_g3_beaconctrlroom.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":117},{"type":"cameraeffect","effect":"Grayscale","amount":"0","keep":"true","id":118},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":119},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":120},{"type":"playmusic","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/avg/m_avg_darkness_03_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":121,"musicid":1},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"1","id":122},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4145_Ulpia_1#1$1","duration":"1.5","isblock":"true","id":123},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":124},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1381_1#8$1","id":125},{"type":"dialogue","name":"布兰都斯","text":"咳咳......你终于来了，乌尔比安。","id":126,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4e/Avg_avg_npc_1381_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4145_Ulpia_1#1$1","id":127},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"你甚至不屑于卖弄你那糟糕的幽默感，为自己辩护？","id":128},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1381_1#8$1","id":129},{"type":"dialogue","name":"布兰都斯","text":"哈哈，糟糕的幽默感——西昆妲也是这么评价我的。","id":130,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4e/Avg_avg_npc_1381_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1381_1#1$1","id":131},{"type":"dialogue","name":"布兰都斯","text":"知道吗，这些年来那个孩子变得越来越像你了。她最终还是会变成另一个你。","id":132,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/0b/Avg_avg_npc_1381_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"布兰都斯","text":"从今往后还会有无数个你，或自愿或不自愿地诞生，前赴后继地投向与海嗣的战争，在战争中毁灭，直到阿戈尔的血都流干。","id":133,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/0b/Avg_avg_npc_1381_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4145_Ulpia_1#5$1","id":134},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"她的变化使我感到悲哀，而你的变化，我甚至难以理解。","id":135},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4145_Ulpia_1#1$1","id":136},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"现在，停下你的动作，交代你们的布局。","id":137},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"深海教徒布兰都斯。","id":138},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1381_1#1$1","id":139},{"type":"dialogue","name":"布兰都斯","text":"你来晚了，我已经没什么动作可以停下了。","id":140,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/0b/Avg_avg_npc_1381_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"布兰都斯","text":"就在刚刚，全息海图接收到了来自第三十七号巢穴的信号。最后一处信标被激活，第Ⅳ级武器已经同步激发。","id":141,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/0b/Avg_avg_npc_1381_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"布兰都斯","text":"你再强大，也没法停下它。","id":142,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/0b/Avg_avg_npc_1381_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1381_1#2$1","id":143},{"type":"dialogue","name":"布兰都斯","text":"如果你想知道深海教会的计划，我也无可奉告。","id":144,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/04/Avg_avg_npc_1381_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1381_1#1$1","id":145},{"type":"dialogue","name":"布兰都斯","text":"他们一厢情愿地处处为我提供掩护，又在某一天突然改变了主意。","id":146,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/0b/Avg_avg_npc_1381_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"布兰都斯","text":"如果没有他们的行动，我可能确实早就被发现了。但我从来没把自己当成他们的一员，我甚至搞不清他们那扭曲的理念。","id":147,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/0b/Avg_avg_npc_1381_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1381_1#8$1","id":148},{"type":"dialogue","name":"布兰都斯","text":"不过，如果你想知道的是我做这些事的缘由，我很愿意讲给你听，乌尔比安。","id":149,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4e/Avg_avg_npc_1381_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4145_Ulpia_1#1$1","id":150},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"很好，这可以为我省去一些不必要的暴力手段。","id":151},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1381_1#8$1","id":152},{"type":"dialogue","name":"布兰都斯","text":"哈哈，暴力手段。","id":153,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4e/Avg_avg_npc_1381_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"布兰都斯","text":"你还是习惯第一时间诉诸暴力，如果你没把自己的处境搞得这么尴尬，发展规划所的那群老家伙可能很愿意和你促膝长谈。","id":154,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4e/Avg_avg_npc_1381_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1381_1#1$1","id":155},{"type":"dialogue","name":"布兰都斯","text":"知道吗？那场战役失败后，你们很快被“确认死亡”，那之后不久，发展规划所找上了我，邀请我重启深海猎人计划。","id":156,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/0b/Avg_avg_npc_1381_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4145_Ulpia_1#1$1","id":157},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"......","id":158},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1381_1#5$1","id":159},{"type":"dialogue","name":"布兰都斯","text":"你还没有机会去看那场战役的伤亡统计，是不是？","id":160,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d4/Avg_avg_npc_1381_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"布兰都斯","text":"你应该看一看的。深海猎人、军团士兵......那样惨痛的牺牲，换来那样戏谑的结果！","id":161,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d4/Avg_avg_npc_1381_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"布兰都斯","text":"暴力对抗从最开始就是死路，深海猎人计划从最开始就是死局。","id":162,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d4/Avg_avg_npc_1381_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"布兰都斯","text":"确实，阿戈尔从来都没有通过粗暴的蒙蔽和宣传来鼓励牺牲，每一位深海猎人计划的受试者都拥有充足的知情权......","id":163,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d4/Avg_avg_npc_1381_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"布兰都斯","text":"可当同胞的牺牲成为天平上的砝码，那么这种牺牲是否出于自由选择，已经无足轻重。","id":164,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d4/Avg_avg_npc_1381_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"布兰都斯","text":"曾经，阿戈尔人的价值在于我们在人生中所积极创造的一切。可如今呢？我们的生命本身，甚至我们的死亡，都被标上了价码。","id":165,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d4/Avg_avg_npc_1381_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4145_Ulpia_1#1$1","id":166},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"我会留下你的陈词，尽管它毫无意义。","id":167},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"布兰都斯，我本以为怀疑和不满会推动你向更深处探索，而不是变得像现在这般，只会软弱地自欺欺人。","id":168},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"每一个堕落者都会或激昂或悲切地发表类似的言论，声称自己看到了阿戈尔的堕落。","id":169},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"为一个国家赋予一套人格，用拟人化的方式去评判它的道德，即使作为博取自我满足的手段来看，也堪称低劣。","id":170},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"倒是你，你在声泪俱下地批判无谓的牺牲时，难道就没想过自己对航道计划的破坏，会夺走多少生命？","id":171},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1381_1#8$1","id":172},{"type":"dialogue","name":"布兰都斯","text":"破坏？","id":173,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4e/Avg_avg_npc_1381_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"布兰都斯","text":"不，乌尔比安，我在尝试开辟一条真正的道路。","id":174,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4e/Avg_avg_npc_1381_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4145_Ulpia_1#1$1","id":175},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"你到底做了什么手脚？","id":176},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1381_1#8$1","id":177},{"type":"dialogue","name":"布兰都斯","text":"别着急，乌尔比安，我都会告诉你。","id":178,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4e/Avg_avg_npc_1381_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":179},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"1","id":180},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","posfrom":"0,0","posto":"-200,0","afrom":"1","ato":"0","duration":"1.5","isblock":"true","id":181},{"type":"text","text":"布兰都斯越过乌尔比安，在巨大的全息海图前停下了脚步。他背对着乌尔比安，手指扫过纷繁的光点，指向右上角正在闪烁的某一处。","id":182},{"type":"charslot","id":183},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1381_1#8$1","focus":"l","id":184},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_4145_Ulpia_1#1$1","focus":"n","id":185},{"type":"dialogue","name":"布兰都斯","text":"看到了吗，猎人们此刻正在这个位置。","id":186},{"type":"dialogue","name":"布兰都斯","text":"她们激活了最后一处信标，此刻可能陷入了苦战，但绝不会有危险......不会有真正的危险。","id":187},{"type":"dialogue","name":"布兰都斯","text":"她们战至力竭的那一刻，就是武器起作用的那一刻——海嗣会停止争斗，拥她们入眠。","id":188},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_4145_Ulpia_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":189},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"说下去。","id":190},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1381_1#8$1","focus":"l","id":191},{"type":"dialogue","name":"布兰都斯","text":"如果你还记得自适应接点技术，你便不难理解我接下来要说的内容。","id":192,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4e/Avg_avg_npc_1381_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_4145_Ulpia_1#5$1","focus":"r","id":193},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"当年在我身上发生的那起手术事故？","id":194},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1381_1#5$1","focus":"l","id":195},{"type":"dialogue","name":"布兰都斯","text":"是。你当时说的没错，它确实具有进一步研究的价值。","id":196,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d4/Avg_avg_npc_1381_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"布兰都斯","text":"自适应接点在你的身体内部，实现了微观层面的平衡。你的身体不再排斥海嗣基因，海嗣基因也奇迹般地停止了对你的影响。","id":197,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d4/Avg_avg_npc_1381_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"布兰都斯","text":"这或许是一种偶然，可我很快发现，我能够在宏观层面上复现这种现象，一定程度上消除海嗣对人类的敌意。","id":198,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d4/Avg_avg_npc_1381_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"布兰都斯","text":"歌蕾蒂娅她们前往第三十七号巢穴之前，我趁那场手术的机会，在她们身上重现了你当年的“手术事故”。","id":199,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d4/Avg_avg_npc_1381_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_4145_Ulpia_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":200},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"......","id":201},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"你想要在猎人们身上复现一种原理未知、效果不明，甚至没有经过严谨验证的“手术事故”？","id":202},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1381_1#8$1","focus":"l","id":203},{"type":"dialogue","name":"布兰都斯","text":"不不不，曾经在你体内出现的现象，已经不再是一种偶然。在你消失的这段时间，我从未有一刻停止对它的研究。","id":204,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4e/Avg_avg_npc_1381_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"布兰都斯","text":"......我相信你们还活着，我相信你们会回来，我可以帮你们摆脱这该死的“命运”。","id":205,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4e/Avg_avg_npc_1381_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_4145_Ulpia_1#6$1","focus":"r","id":206},{"type":"multiline","name":"乌尔比安","text":"你明明拒绝了重启深海猎人计划，你是怎么......","id":207},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_4145_Ulpia_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":208},{"type":"multiline","name":"乌尔比安","end":"true","text":"你在自己的身上做实验？","id":209},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"难怪你的身上透着一股死气。","id":210},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1381_1#8$1","focus":"l","id":211},{"type":"dialogue","name":"布兰都斯","text":"哈哈，我的身体条件自然和你没法比。","id":212,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4e/Avg_avg_npc_1381_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"布兰都斯","text":"我的时间已经不多，咳咳......我甚至能清晰地感受到生命在流逝......但还好，该做的事情都已经做完。","id":213,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4e/Avg_avg_npc_1381_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"布兰都斯","text":"告诉我，乌尔比安，深海猎人是作为一种解决方案诞生的，而不是一种工具、一种武器、一种注定被抛弃的消耗品。","id":214,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4e/Avg_avg_npc_1381_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_4145_Ulpia_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":215},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"是。","id":216},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1381_1#9$1","focus":"l","id":217},{"type":"dialogue","name":"布兰都斯","text":"......好。","id":218,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/eb/Avg_avg_npc_1381_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1381_1#8$1","focus":"l","id":219},{"type":"dialogue","name":"布兰都斯","text":"深海猎人计划已经失败，但猎人们如今仍有机会完成自己作为解决方案的使命，不过不是通过杀戮与牺牲。","id":220,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4e/Avg_avg_npc_1381_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"布兰都斯","text":"你们会活着发挥自己的价值，而不是用牺牲换取阿戈尔的苟延残喘。","id":221,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4e/Avg_avg_npc_1381_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"布兰都斯","text":"以深海猎人为起点，人类与海嗣的关系将被改写。如果我能让海嗣视猎人们为亲族，我或许也能让大群视阿戈尔为友邻。","id":222,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4e/Avg_avg_npc_1381_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_4145_Ulpia_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":223},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"所以你盯上了航道计划。","id":224},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1381_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":225},{"type":"dialogue","name":"布兰都斯","text":"准确说，是航道计划找上了我。","id":226,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/0b/Avg_avg_npc_1381_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"布兰都斯","text":"几乎与发展规划所同时，克莱门莎也找到了我。她向我介绍了航道计划的布局，以及第Ⅳ级武器的研发计划。","id":227,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/0b/Avg_avg_npc_1381_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"布兰都斯","text":"这种以生物技术为核心的武器可以大规模地影响海嗣行为，它在底层原理上与自适应接点技术有着天然的相似性。","id":228,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/0b/Avg_avg_npc_1381_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"布兰都斯","text":"当时，我已经完成了自适应接点的技术积累，甚至，它的应用对象已经不再局限于人体。","id":229,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/0b/Avg_avg_npc_1381_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"布兰都斯","text":"所以，我对第Ⅳ级武器进行了一点小小的改造。当它启动的那一刻，我们与海嗣的争斗或许就能告一段落。","id":230,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/0b/Avg_avg_npc_1381_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"布兰都斯","text":"无论是深海猎人，还是第Ⅳ级武器，都将跨越物种的隔阂，成为一条道路，一座桥梁。","id":231,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/0b/Avg_avg_npc_1381_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1381_1#7$1","focus":"l","id":232},{"type":"dialogue","name":"布兰都斯","text":"多么讽刺，阿戈尔与海嗣持续两百多年的战争，只靠一点小小的手脚，就可能被停下来。","id":233,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/df/Avg_avg_npc_1381_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"布兰都斯","text":"或许从一开始，这场战争的严肃性就是虚构的。我无意对前人的作为大加评判，但至少我们还有机会选择另一种可能性。","id":234,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/df/Avg_avg_npc_1381_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_4145_Ulpia_1#8$1","focus":"r","id":235},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"......","id":236},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1381_1#8$1","focus":"l","id":237},{"type":"dialogue","name":"布兰都斯","text":"但我已经时日无多，我能做的也仅限于此......幸运的是，我终于在斗智场看到了你。","id":238,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4e/Avg_avg_npc_1381_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"布兰都斯","text":"你是深海猎人计划的发起者，你熟悉自适应接点，你经历了这一切，唯有你，乌尔比安，唯有你可以让这项事业延续下去。","id":239,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4e/Avg_avg_npc_1381_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_4145_Ulpia_1#8$1","focus":"r","id":240},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"所以你才这么坦然地等着我找上门来，在死前向我托付你的“事业”？","id":241},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1381_1#8$1","focus":"l","id":242},{"type":"dialogue","name":"布兰都斯","text":"这次轮到我邀请你了。阿戈尔与海嗣有机会实现共生共荣，或许你愿意见证那个未来？","id":243,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4e/Avg_avg_npc_1381_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_4145_Ulpia_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":244},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"我拒绝。","id":245},{"type":"dialog","id":246},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":247},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1381_1#4$1","focus":"l","id":248},{"type":"dialogue","name":"布兰都斯","text":"虽然在意料之中，但你的回答未免也太干脆了。","id":249,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/16/Avg_avg_npc_1381_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"布兰都斯","text":"乌尔比安，我会死在这间中控室，但......","id":250,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/16/Avg_avg_npc_1381_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_4145_Ulpia_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":251},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"布兰都斯，哪怕你的死亡已经注定，你也必须要知道，你没有资格带着遗憾、带着不甘死去。","id":252},{"type":"dialog","id":253},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":254},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":255},{"type":"charslot","id":256},{"type":"background","id":257},{"type":"curtain","direction":"6","fillfrom":"0.6","fillto":"0.6","fadetime":"1","id":258},{"type":"curtain","direction":"2","fillfrom":"0.1","fillto":"0.1","fadetime":"1","id":259},{"type":"image","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/77/Avg_51_i06_1.png","screenadapt":"coverall","x":"0","xScale":"1.1","yScale":"1.1","fadetime":"0","id":260},{"type":"imagetween","xFrom":"50","xTo":"-100","duration":"25","block":"false","id":261},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":262},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":263},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"曾几何时，我们试图通过研究阿戈尔人自身的细胞演化历程，梳理我们存在的意义。","id":264},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"但为了一个虚无缥缈的妄想，你已经亲手摧毁了自己的一切。","id":265},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"海嗣是荼毒海洋的渣滓，这一点毋庸置疑。","id":266},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"它们更是充满未知的生物，而你却相信自己能与它们像朋友一样“共生共荣”？","id":267},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"布兰都斯，这和以前的阿戈尔人笃定自己能战胜它们一样傲慢。不，要傲慢百倍。","id":268},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"你清楚自己在想什么吗？你在所谓“共生共荣”的幻想中，期望看到的是怎样的景象？","id":269},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"海嗣是要成为童话故事中神秘的海底仙灵，还是要成为人人爱不释手的家养宠物？","id":270},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"歌蕾蒂娅与海嗣辩论哲学？斯卡蒂与海嗣共进下午茶？劳伦缇娜与海嗣相拥着跳舞？","id":271},{"type":"dialog","id":272},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":273},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":274},{"type":"curtain","direction":"6","fillfrom":"0.1","fillto":"0.1","fadetime":"1","id":275},{"type":"curtain","direction":"2","fillfrom":"0.6","fillto":"0.6","fadetime":"1","id":276},{"type":"image","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/77/Avg_51_i06_1.png","screenadapt":"coverall","x":"0","xScale":"1.1","yScale":"1.1","fadetime":"0","id":277},{"type":"imagetween","xFrom":"0","xTo":"-80","duration":"20","block":"false","id":278},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":279},{"type":"dialogue","name":"布兰都斯","text":"......","id":280},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"......","id":281},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"你甚至无法清晰地描绘出哪怕一个画面，是不是？","id":282},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"你连自己作为科学家的专业素养也丢掉了。布兰都斯，现在的你令人发笑。","id":283},{"type":"dialogue","name":"布兰都斯","text":"乌尔比安，你从来没有一口气说过那么多话。","id":284},{"type":"dialogue","name":"布兰都斯","text":"你是想说，令人失望吧？","id":285},{"type":"dialog","id":286},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":287},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":288},{"type":"curtain","id":289},{"type":"image","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/77/Avg_51_i06_1.png","screenadapt":"coverall","xScale":"1.1","yScale":"1.1","fadetime":"0","id":290},{"type":"imagetween","xScaleFrom":"1.1","yScaleFrom":"1.1","xScaleTo":"1","yScaleTo":"1","duration":"30","block":"false","id":291},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":292},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":293},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"失望的从来都只有你自己，布兰都斯。","id":294},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"所以，你没有资格带着遗憾、带着不甘死在我面前。","id":295},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"每一个堕落者都应该接受审判，每一个堕落者的尸体都应该被挂在干燥的礁石上。","id":296},{"type":"dialogue","name":"布兰都斯","text":"......你还能审判我吗？","id":297},{"type":"dialogue","name":"布兰都斯","text":"斩杀“初生”的战役疑点重重，你已经成为最大的嫌疑人，而你如今的种种行径，已经让你站在了阿戈尔的对面——","id":298},{"type":"dialogue","name":"布兰都斯","text":"你已经被这个国家抛弃。","id":299},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"所以我只能接过你的事业？","id":300},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"布兰都斯，以前的你，可说不出这套阴谋家的话术。","id":301},{"type":"dialogue","name":"布兰都斯","text":"我只是在陈述客观事实。","id":302},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"那么此时此刻，即是我最后一次作为一个阿戈尔人，对你下达判决。","id":303},{"type":"dialogue","name":"布兰都斯","text":"......","id":304},{"type":"dialog","id":305},{"type":"text","text":"布兰都斯不再应答，或许是失去了力气，或许是放弃了反驳。这场前言不搭后语的对话已经拖得太久，久到令他开始感到疲惫。","id":306},{"type":"text","text":"金色的海图在他眼前荡漾。太晃眼了——他这样想着，闭上了眼睛。","id":307},{"type":"dialog","id":308},{"type":"image","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3c/Avg_51_i06_2.png","screenadapt":"coverall","fadetime":"2","id":309},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":310},{"type":"playsound","key":"$transmission","volume":"1","id":311},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":312},{"type":"text","text":"不知来由的通讯唐突地打破了短暂的寂静，与此同时，他听见故友的巨锚在地面上划出锐响。","id":313},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_ironchaindrop","volume":"1","id":314},{"type":"text","text":"而他只来得及想起，自己甚至还没来得及给归乡的猎人们一个拥抱。","id":315},{"type":"dialog","id":316},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":317},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"4","block":"true","id":318},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":319},{"type":"charslot","id":320},{"type":"background","id":321},{"type":"image","id":322}],"characters":["布兰都斯","乌尔比安"]}